    public static class DescriptorEntitySet.EntitySetBase<T>
extends java.util.HashSet<T>
implements Axiom.EntitySet<T>
    Base interface for all the DescriptorEntitySet that extends EntitySet.

    This class implements common features for managing an HashSet and a singleton value for EntitySet.
